<%= render 'hero' %>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row p-5">
    <div class="col-lg-10 offset-lg-1">
      <h4 class="text-orange text-bold mb-3">Send a Wuphf Now:</h4>
      <%= render 'form' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-purple text-white p-5">
  <div class="container">
    <%= image_tag("dog_bubble.svg",size: "200", alt: "That's What She Said!", class: "img-fluid pb-2") %>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-bold"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-refresh"></i> Turned Tables</h4>
        <p class="text-left mb-3">
          That's right, the turn tables. Worried that your friends aren't seeing your messages? Or maybe they're ignoring you. By registering for WUPHF.io you can be sure to blast all of their lines in one go. Email? Covered. Text? We got that too. Twitter? Oh yeah. Facebook? Well... that's coming soon.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-bold"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-calculator"></i> Numbers Crunched</h4>
        <p class="text-left mb-3">
          Sign up today and we'll crunch all of the numbers for you. What numbers do you need crunching? Because we'll crunch them and we'll crunch them good. What does that have to do with WUPHF? I don't know, you tell me.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-bold"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-bank"></i> Bankruptcy Declared</h4>
        <p class="text-left mb-3">
          Having a hard time declaring bankruptcy? WUPHF is a great place to declare bankruptcy to all of your friends and family. In fact, you can WUPHF about your bankruptcy to people who aren't your friends - as long as they're in your Dog Pack. Oh yeah, I should talk about the DOG PACK. Register to find out more
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <h1 class="cta text-center"><em>Let's WUPHF together</em></h1>
    <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: "text-white" do %>
      <section class="text-center">
        <button class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-primary text-white border-white mt-3">Get Started Today</button>
      </section>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<% content_for :page_js do %>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    <%= render file: "#{Rails.root}/app/views/demo_wuphfs/js/call_to_action.js" %>
  </script>
<% end %>
